comments: Siakam (TOR) briefly places an arm around Kaminsky (CHA) and immediately slides it off.
Siakam (TOR) makes marginal contact with Walker (CHA) on the perimeter that does not affect his SQBR.
Green (TOR) makes incidental contact with Walker (CHA) after he makes the pass.
Green (TOR) makes marginal contact with Walker (CHA) that does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
Graham (CHA) makes contact with Leonard's (TOR) arm and the contact affects his play at the basket.
Siakam (TOR) jumps vertically contesting Lamb's (CHA) driving shot attempt and the contact to the body is considered incidental.  Green (TOR) cleanly blocks the shot attempt.
Walker (CHA) makes incidental contact with Leonard's (TOR) arm during the rebound.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of Raptors possession stands as called.
Leonard (TOR) legally contests the driving shot attempt by Walker (CHA) and makes clean contact with the ball.
Leonard (TOR) blocks the shot attempt by Walker (CHA) before it reaches its apex.
Bridges (CHA) legally contests Leonard's (TOR) jump shot attempt.  Any high-five contact after the release is considered incidental.
VanVleet (TOR) commits a take foul on Bridges (CHA).
Siakam (TOR) makes clean contact with the ball and any contact to the body of Lamb (CHA) is considered incidental.
Lamb (CHA) legally retrieves the ball in the backcourt after Siakam (TOR) makes contact with it.
